                                        <p class="paragraph xl:p2 xs:p3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                                            By accessing and using this website, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provisions of this agreement. These terms apply to all visitors, users, and others who access or use the website.
                                        </p>
                                        <p class="paragraph xl:p2 xs:p3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                                            Your continued use of the website following the posting of any changes to these terms constitutes acceptance of those changes.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    
